        <item>
            <title>Clop Ziben v4.1.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 13:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>4.1.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>4.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Clop Ziben v4.1.0</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Feat: restored Ziben image + video presets (Web default) with menubar selector</li>
                    <li>Feat: pre-seeded PresetZones (8 drop targets) for ctrl-drag</li>
                    <li>Perf: single source of truth — same Pipelines power menubar + drop zones</li>
                    <li>Perf: cwebp uses active preset quality, -preset icon, -mt multithread</li>
                    <li>Perf: HEVC -q:v driven by active video preset quality</li>
                    <li>Perf: resize skips intermediate pngquant when WebP convert follows (2 passes vs 3)</li>
                    <li>Fix: "Unknown image type" after WebP convert (optimise() now handles WebP/AVIF/HEIC)</li>
                    <li>Fix: "Resizing to WxH" overlay lingering — now reuses main pipeline optimiser id</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
